race.comment: JUSTACCLAIM (2) is a Dark Acclaim gelding on debut for the Hannemann camp. Has shown encouraging signs in his lead-up work. Needs some luck from the wide draw but can make a bright start. GERACE (8) was much better last start at Clare when sent forward, only to be run down late. Draws low again and can give another bold sight. ROYOLO (11) improved second-up at Clare when sent forward, also getting grabbed late. Strips fitter and should be in this for a long way from the draw. ALABAMA BELLE (7) resumes and is worth monitoring in the betting.
